long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Automobile Vehicle Sports Car Live Wallpaper transforms your Chrome into a racing-inspired experience. Featuring a high-performance sports car set against a bold and vibrant backdrop, this live wallpaper is perfect for car enthusiasts and speed lovers.

Key Features:
🚗 Dynamic Design: A stylish sports car in vivid detail that brings energy to your new tab.
🔍 Search at Your Fingertips: Use your default search engine directly from the new tab.
🕒 Time & Date Display: Stay on track with an integrated clock and calendar.
🔗 Shortcut Customization: Easily manage and personalize your frequently visited sites.
✨ Smooth Animations: Enjoy seamless transitions and immersive visuals.
Elevate your Chrome with this high-octane design that combines elegance and excitement for automobile enthusiasts.
